Wait, make that waffles.
Scratch that.

14:02.675 --> 14:04.676
Make it pancake mix
in a waffle maker.

14:04.677 --> 14:06.611
That's what waffles are, Gene.

14:06.612 --> 14:08.145
They're...
that's pancakes in a...

14:08.180 --> 14:09.414
I don't want a conversation.

14:09.415 --> 14:11.148
I want pancakes
in the shape of waffles.

14:11.183 --> 14:13.218
Okay, fine.
Big day.

14:13.219 --> 14:15.586
I can't wait to see your
Thanksgiving play.

14:15.621 --> 14:17.888
Oh, it's gonna be
a real showstopper, Mom.

14:17.923 --> 14:19.190
I bet it is.

14:19.191 --> 14:20.691
Are you excited, Tina?

14:20.726 --> 14:22.127
Um, yeah, totally.

14:22.128 --> 14:24.596
For sure, totally.
Of course she is!

14:24.597 --> 14:26.730
Look at her, she can
barely contain herself.

14:26.766 --> 14:28.066
We're really proud
of you kids.

14:28.067 --> 14:30.901
