this year?

15:35.801 --> 15:37.335
I wouldn't read into it.

15:37.336 --> 15:38.970
Yeah, you're right.

15:38.971 --> 15:41.139
(off-key):
♪ We're going to dinner ♪

15:41.140 --> 15:43.141
♪ We're going
to dinner ♪

