15:58.524 --> 16:00.959
Aw, Bobby.
(clears throat)

16:00.960 --> 16:03.628
I'm just holding him up
so he could see his grandkids.

16:03.629 --> 16:05.063
Is he blocking you?
Uh, yeah.

16:05.064 --> 16:06.564
Thanks, you're a doll.
It's a potato

16:06.565 --> 16:08.298
that looks
like her grandfather.

16:08.334 --> 16:09.901
I don't know, it doesn't look
like a face to me.

16:09.902 --> 16:11.903
Well, it's dark in
here, so... but it does.

16:11.904 --> 16:13.838
Okay, but I still...
Lin, show him a picture

16:13.839 --> 16:15.506
