He's trying to watch the show.

16:15.541 --> 16:18.843
♪ Why can't I be like
the other turkeys? ♪

16:18.844 --> 16:21.746
♪ They're all off having fun ♪

16:21.747 --> 16:25.282
♪ Is it 'cause I'm scrawny
