(keyboard plays drumroll)
Yeah! Ow, ow.

16:34.026 --> 16:36.761
♪ Man, oh, man,
I dig that pig ♪

16:36.762 --> 16:37.896
Hey, turkey.

16:37.897 --> 16:39.296
I'm too quirky;
don't look at me!

16:39.331 --> 16:40.331
Okay.

16:40.332 --> 16:41.899
