Air compressor,
this is your big debut.

16:46.438 --> 16:48.206
(quiet electrical hum)

16:48.207 --> 16:49.841
Uh-oh!

16:49.842 --> 16:52.410
I'm starting to suspect
we're not just going to dinner,

16:52.411 --> 16:54.011
