a good idea.

17:48.801 --> 17:51.703
Tina, I'm so sorry. You put
in all this work, and now I...

17:51.704 --> 17:53.838
Louise, we got to
keep doing the show.

17:53.873 --> 17:55.306
Excuse me?

17:55.341 --> 17:56.475
The musical
was missing something.

17:56.476 --> 17:57.976
