to be part of this.

19:19.259 --> 19:20.224
Oh, God.

19:20.260 --> 19:22.027
She's so quirky.

19:22.028 --> 19:23.262
I'm quirky, too, right?

19:23.263 --> 19:24.695
You wish.
What?!

19:24.731 --> 19:27.199
♪ I'm happy to be who I am ♪

19:27.200 --> 19:32.137
♪ Now I'm gonna see about a pig
