19:32.138 --> 19:33.739
Hey, quirky turkey.

19:33.740 --> 19:36.275
I've been looking
for you everywhere.

19:36.276 --> 19:37.743
Shut your snout
and kiss me.

19:37.744 --> 19:40.578
