19:40.613 --> 19:41.746
Oh, oh, boy.

19:41.781 --> 19:43.915
Okay, maybe now
we shut it down.

19:43.916 --> 19:45.484
Do you think they'll make us
clean this up?

19:45.485 --> 19:46.818
Yeah, I think they will.

19:46.819 --> 19:48.587
We're not gonna get
that half day, are we?

19:48.588 --> 19:49.553
Nope.

19:49.589 --> 19:51.355
Worth it.
Totally worth it.

